  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Ypeginterferon Alfa-2b in HBeAg Positive Chronic Hepatitis B</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Open-label and Positive Controlled Phase II Clinical Trial to Assess Efficacy and Safety of Ypeginterferon Alfa-2b in HBeAg Positive Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B</official_title>
